    "However, this approach was computationally expensive.",
    "Faster ReCNN was proposed in 2015 [17,18], aiming to improve both speed and precision by introducing the region proposal network (RPN) and Region of Interest (ROI) pooling.",
    "Various network models have been derived from Faster ReCNN to address different problem domains.",
    "However, these models inherit some limitations from ReCNN and Faster ReCNN.",
    "The two-stage design of these models makes inference slower due to separate proposal generation and detection steps."
